1. Buttons to add on the screens:
   Library -> Directory screen
   ==========================
      * Add to Playlist
   Library -> Song
   ==========================
      * Add to Playlist
   Playlist
   ==========================
      * Save Playlist

2. New screen/window:
   Add to Playlist
   =================
   List all Playlists in the system + <Create New Playlist> at the bottom of the list to create a new playlist (will require an onscreen keyboard)
